  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242047.htm", 
  "description": "<p> <strong>谷歌</strong><strong>YouTube打算推出一项向导计划，帮助广告客户制定它们的YouTube内容战略。</strong>据悉，这项新的向导计划只针对品牌厂商提供，它也可以说是谷歌Brand Labs服务的一项拓展服务。Brand Labs服务的目的也是帮助广告客户制定YouTube内容战略，但是新计划将更加专注于帮助那些真正地创造有吸引力的内容的品牌厂商。 </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2da093b5/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242047.htm&amp;t=YouTube%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E6%8E%A8%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%90%91%E5%AF%BC%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242047.htm&amp;t=YouTube%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E6%8E%A8%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%90%91%E5%AF%BC%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242047.htm&amp;t=YouTube%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E6%8E%A8%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%90%91%E5%AF%BC%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242047.htm&amp;t=YouTube%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%8E%82%E5%95%86%E6%8E%A8%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%90%91%E5%AF%BC%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242047.htm&amp;t=YouTube%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B