  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242046.htm", 
  "description": "<p>&#160; &#160;<strong>腾讯和南非传媒巨头Naspers正大幅投资印度科技市场，双方的合资公司Ibibo现已收购在线车票公司redBus.in。</strong>Ibibo透露，交易细节尚未公布，但收购价格约为1.35亿美元。目前，Naspers持有Ibibo 80%的股份，腾讯持有20%。双方很可能以此为契机，将Redbus的平台和业务模式引入中国等市场。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2da093b4/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242046.htm&amp;t=%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%90%88%E8%B5%84%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%ADRedBus\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242046.htm&amp;t=%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%90%88%E8%B5%84%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%ADRedBus\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242046.htm&amp;t=%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%90%88%E8%B5%84%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%ADRedBus\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242046.htm&amp;t=%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%90%88%E8%B5%84%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%ADRedBus\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242046.htm&amp;t=%E8%85%BE%E8%AE%AF%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%90%88%E8%B5%84%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%ADRedBus\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\" /></a></td><td valign=\"middl